longBusinessSummary: Industrial Nanotech, Inc. develops and manufactures nanotechnology in the United States. It also operates manufacturing facilities. The company markets under Syneffex, Anaconda, and Talking paint brands. The company serves food and beverage processing, chemical and petrochemical plants, equipment manufacturing factories, agriculture, pulp and paper mills, and maritime industries. Industrial Nanotech, Inc. is based in Broomfield, Colorado.
